title: Hell 1.1 chess opening book
description:
Book was created by derivation of top class games from ICCF server (International Corespondence Chess Federation server).
All games are evaluated by top engines like Stockfish, Komodo and Houdini for hours and days with ideas from real human GMs handling them.

Recommended
- default settings - 2/100
- for any engine vs. engine competition
- for any chess match with engines use allowed

Do not use for testing engines!

Change log for v1.1
- updated game database
- more top qulity games added
- fresh compile with better settings

Created and distributed by maelic
